						<li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share tagmanager" title="Share by Email" href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0ASouth Africa Is Taking a Huge Swing to Save Its Imperiled Penguins%0D%0AThe question now is, Will it work?%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/news/south-africa-is-taking-a-huge-swing-to-save-its-imperiled-penguins/" target="_blank"><span>Share by Email</span></a></li>



					</ul>
